  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 49-7-181, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO CREATE THE WILD TURKEY STAMP FUND AS A SPECIAL FUND WITHIN THE STATE TREASURY; TO PROVIDE THAT ALL REVENUE COLLECTED FROM THE PROCEEDS OF WILD TURKEY STAMPS SHALL BE DEPOSITED INTO SUCH FUND AND SHALL BE DESIGNATED FOR USE BY THE DEPARTMENT OF WILDLIFE, FISHERIES AND PARKS ONLY FOR CERTAIN OBJECTIVES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
